# INDEX
POST http://localhost:3000/indexes/books
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "config": {
    "fields": ["title", "author"],
    "storeFields": ["id", "title", "author", "publicationYear"],
    "idField": "id"
  },
  "documents": [
    { "id": "b1", "title": "Dune", "author": "Frank Herbert", "publicationYear": 1965 },
    { "id": "b2", "title": "Foundation", "author": "Isaac Asimov", "publicationYear": 1951 }
  ]
}
### SEARCH
GET http://localhost:3000/indexes/books/search?query=Dune

### SEARCH WITH FILTER
POST http://localhost:3000/indexes/books/search

{
  "query": "Dune",
  "limit": 5,
  "filter": { "publicationYear": 1965 }
}

### GET SUGGESTIONS (AUTO COMPLETE)
GET http://localhost:3000/indexes/books/suggest?query=Dune

### LIST INDEXES
GET http://localhost:3000/indexes

### DELETE INDEX
DELETE http://localhost:3000/indexes/books

